Ep.08 "RIVALRY WITH GRANDMA TOYO"

529
00:42:56,567 --> 00:43:00,667
{\an8}We start training at the hospital
next week. I'm so nervous.

530
00:43:02,700 --> 00:43:04,000
I'm sure she's a really sweet old lady!

531
00:43:04,167 --> 00:43:06,100
You two may get along well.

532
00:43:06,167 --> 00:43:08,600
I can't be remembering trainee's names.

533
00:43:08,700 --> 00:43:11,567
She called me 8 times
this morning alone!

534
00:43:11,667 --> 00:43:13,033
She's a bully!

535
00:43:14,733 --> 00:43:17,033
I'm losing confidence.

536
00:43:17,367 --> 00:43:19,433
Are you going to quit?

537
00:43:20,233 --> 00:43:21,067
